title: RHOC's Brooks Ayers Parties After Vicki Gunvalson Split, Rumors of Faking Cancer (Sierra Marquina/Us Weekly)
content:
Sierra Marquina / Us Weekly:
RHOC's Brooks Ayers Parties After Vicki Gunvalson Split, Rumors of Faking Cancer  —  Brooks Ayers spent Saturday, Sept. 26, whooping it up — just without his ex-girlfriend Vicki Gunvalson, who introduced the Real Housewives of Orange County phrase.  Multiple sources tell Us Weekly exclusively …
